title: Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile"
description: In the present lightly sketched view, the female head is inclined downward. Wavy hair frames the face. The downcast eye, shaded, and slightly smiling mouth are the salient facial features.

tombstone.epitaph:
Drawing, "Female Head, Left Profile".
20 x 16 cm (8 x 6 5/16 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-91.
